      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "U-556把頭埋在雙腿裡，團坐在椅子上。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "不知道時間過去了多久",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "指揮官也知道的吧？我曾經說過，我和俾斯麥大姐有個“約定”。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-2",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "無論在哪裡，只要姐姐遇到了危險，我都一定會去保護她。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "仔細想想，這個約定本身就很奇怪吧？一個潛水艇，說要保護好戰列艦什麼的…這怎麼可能做得到啦，哈哈。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "而我確還在天天拿著這個約定當藉口，不停打擾俾斯麥姐姐……",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "我真是太任性了啊。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "不過沒關係，俾斯麥姐姐說過的，不好的習慣只要能夠及時改正。接下來我會更加用心對待自己的任務的。當然了，有機會的話，我也要幫上姐姐的忙，為她分擔壓力",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 4,
      "say": "不……說對不起的應該是我。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "say": "俾斯麥姐姐？！為什麼妳會在這裡？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-2",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "因為和指揮官一樣擔心妳，就一起跟過來了。剛才說的話讓妳感到困擾是我不好，抱歉。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "paintingFadeOut": {
        "time": 0.5,
        "side": 0
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "沒有沒有，怎麼會呢，說到底還是我太任性打擾了姐姐——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 3,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "不對哦。我從來沒有覺得“妳是在打擾我”，一次都沒有。",
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "倒不如說，其實我很享受與妳交談的時光。和妳在一起的時候，我能暫時放下鐵血艦隊領袖的身份與職責，享受片刻的閒適與安寧。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "“原來我也可以是這麼簡單純粹的角色”，U-556總會給我這種的感覺呢。",
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "……",
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "說實話，我沒想到妳會如此奮不顧身地衝過來，只為履行當初那個玩笑般的約定……",
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "妳不是一位給別人添麻煩的孩子，而是一位對諾言對忠心不二的，值得尊敬的騎士。應該感到慚愧的，是沒能及時覺察到妳這份心情的我。對不起",
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "俾斯麥突然站直了起來，清了清嗓子。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 4,
      "say": "U-556！令人尊敬的水下騎士啊。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 405010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "如果我遇到了危險，妳還會幫助我嗎？即使自己也會因此陷入無法挽回的境地？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "U-556楞了一下，隨即露出了燦爛的笑容。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 408040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "blackBg": true,
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "嗯！不論在任何地方，不管身處何種險境，我都會保護好俾斯麥姐姐的！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
